5:44:28.000Z","msg":"比管理層食好d都正常<br />\n但平過工人飯盒就真係幾唔合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0957333157cd9ffe692fb658e743e8e5d9ee18a","tid":149856,"uid":13116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"31蚊<br />\n有中（三選二餸菜）/西餐肉醬意粉之類<br />\n有湯 生果 香蕉蘋果<br />\n我認為入得口<br />\n不過較老果啲未必岩食另計<br />\n都好平 食得幾開心"},{"pid":"cc4d19d5fb78c7bbcba5890a18019c75608dc20f","tid":149856,"uid":30070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"外判要31蚊 係因為冇食飯津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c137a69378a8c3e49c9dca25a7147fa83aa889","tid":149856,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:20:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e45b01b56b1cba5bbfcfa4a230e21e023f812577","tid":149856,"uid":1190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"2間都做過，clp 個飯堂冇今階級。港燈最高級果間食西餐，有侍應服侍"},{"pid":"041200d91a8c5d7798d80873107b4476d0856252","tid":149856,"uid":21402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"Sodexo?<br />\n外判33.5 白飯例湯任裝<br />\n好難食"},{"pid":"538596b9ae62601bfb274e91b354b94339b8a542","tid":149856,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"食好啲仲平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理西啲垃圾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}